//lihkg.com/thread/2382161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2382161</a><br />\n173. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2387672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2387672</a><br />\n174. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2390481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2390481</a><br />\n175. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2391905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2391905</a><br />\n176. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2395884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2395884</a><br />\n177. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2400063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2400063</a><br />\n178. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2401344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2401344</a><br />\n179. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2403873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2403873</a><br />\n180. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2405689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2405689</a><br />\n181. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2407745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2407745</a><br />\n182. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2409284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2409284</a><br />\n183. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2414540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2414540</a><br />\n184. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2415142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2415142</a><br />\n185. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2420127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2420127</a><br />\n186. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2428198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2428198</a><br />\n187. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2440073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2440073</a><br />\n188. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2448149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2448149</a><br />\n189. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2457163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2457163</a><br />\n190. <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2467001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2467001</a><br />\n金句:<br />\nFor 普通分手<br />\n分手之後，應該忘記就要忘記! 調整好自己既心情，讓自己早日得到解脫。<br />\n放低真係要完完全全去靠自己，時間係最好既方法。<br />\n咩承諾呀乜乜柒柒 當一個人唔再鐘意你 要同你分手既話，呢啲所有一切既野都係廢。<br />\n你都識講係你自己做得唔好啦 仲想人地番黎你身邊 害死人呀你<br />\n你咪當今次拍拖比你學到唔同既野囉 下次咪唔好重覆你上次拍拖個陣做既錯事囉<br />\n<br />\nFor 被出軌<br />\n唔明點解啲人要出軌<br />\n細水長流唔好咩，變左親人咁唔好咩<br />\n點解硬係要做一啲嘢黎傷害果個陪左你咁耐嘅人<br />\n新鮮感係會有，但知道開始有呢種感覺都好應該避忌啦<br />\n點解唔係去避忌<br />\n要一直玩火<br />\n有幾多人明白新鮮感總會淡 又有幾多人明白感情係要維繫而唔係一唔開心就換個第二個？<br />\n正所謂係鐘意佢嘅，又點會要佢傷心<br />\n<br />\n仆街賤男心態<br />\n同你相處得唔舒服&gt;得佢辛苦你做錯曬&gt; 我可以去偷食 因為同錯人拍拖&gt; 比你發現&gt; 擺牌&gt; 做好人放你走&gt; 你值得搵更好既人&gt; 我走啦88<br />\n<br />\n散咗無曬動力<br />\n係時候要準備行出去感受番個世界<br />\n時間係最好既藥 發生左就係發生左<br />\n世界好大，你可以掛住佢 但同時可以慢慢企起身 去睇下外面原來有山有水有朋友有屋企人<br />\n佢都搵到方法move on了 你呢？<br />\n可以揀留守 等佢既 但首先你個世界要長期出太陽可以溫暖到佢吸引番佢入番你個世界<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />沉多幾日好啦 頂唔順上黎傾下計訓下教吸下正能量啦<br />\n太得閒可以去爬番1-190文 爬完你心情應該會分散左dd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好成日諗點解佢唔想解決問題/點解佢都係唔覆我/點解我低曬頭佢都唔肯返轉頭<br />\n因為唔夠愛你<br />\n<br />\n- 唔好問點解對方咁快放低，因為佢唔愛你了<br />\n- 唔好問點解自己仲未放低，因為放低需要時間，唔洗特別迫自己，掛住佢既就繼續掛，想睇佢啲野既就去睇，之後佢就會慢慢從你既生活消失㗎喇<br />\n- 唔好再諗以前點點點，所有野都已成過去，向前望好過啦<br />\n每個人都有自己既價值<br />\n記住記住 要好好生活落去<br />\n<br />\nv仔金句:<br />\n1. 分手後，唔洗急住放低，慢慢就會好返。<br />\n<br />\n2.同時間，亦都唔洗急住拍拖，唔好揾人做你水泡。<br />\n<br />\n3.唔好放棄自己，唔食野唔返工都好，請努力生存。<br />\n<br />\n4.想喊就喊，想揾朋友就揾，唔好驚煩到人，係你真心朋友既話點都會聽你講。<br />\n<br />\n5.做啲令自己開心既野，食野煲劇訓教都好，總之要令自己忙啲。<br />\n<br />\n6.唔好成日諗住以後會揾唔到好似ex既人，又講話以後唔敢識人呢啲說話，呢個post已經有唔少人出左pool，點解你唔得？<br />\n<br />\n7.愛自己，愛自己，愛自己。<br />\n<br />\n8.揾唔到人傾就上呢個post傾，實有人覆你，呢到基本上係24小時都有人覆你。(((無錯，呢到啲人唔洗訓<br />\n<br />\n我愛香港 香港是我家"},{"pid":"bd56488269454d9c2e90c66a5986ddf56c8b23a0","tid":2476444,"uid":270548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"揮手"},{"pid":"9fe1e98c4a4f874a42dec3fc05486bdba80884e5","tid":2476444,"uid":114618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd56488269454d9c2e90c66a5986ddf56c8b23a0","tid":2476444,"uid":270548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"揮手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f162bab61154b9ac16846b01d39077c1b06c5d8","tid":2476444,"uid":341758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f76664dff22e0b2b1edcf9f7cfba78e171dc60e","tid":2476444,"uid":237530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187cc7929ae4656fb8b40d3970afbf0713c35612","tid":2476444,"uid":241413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T23:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2c9e01708e15cffeab9e7bfaa36502e1ffabbe","tid":2476444,"uid":140348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T01:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4098d7a9db4666e56c57ddfe3fb349289ed492c4","tid":2476444,"uid":272422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:15:45.000Z","msg":"吸收正能量"},{"pid":"b3d4d7dcc289a2796bfebb62e33043cf9e4900ba","tid":2476444,"uid":23431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T10:25:32.000Z